00277 static void mdlOutputs(SimStruct *S, int_T tid)
00278 {
00279         #ifndef __DSPACE__
00280         using namespace qpOASES;
00281         #endif
00282 
00283         int i;
00284         int nV, nC, status;
00285 
00286         int nWSR = NWSR;
00287         int nU   = NCONTROLINPUTS;

00289         InputRealPtrsType in_H, in_g, in_A, in_lb, in_ub, in_lbA, in_ubA;
00290 
00291         SQProblem* problem;
00292         real_t *H, *g, *A, *lb, *ub, *lbA, *ubA, *count;
00293 
00294         real_t *xOpt;

00296         real_T *out_objVal, *out_xOpt, *out_status, *out_nWSR;
00297 
00298 
00299         /* get pointers to block inputs ... */
00300         in_H   = ssGetInputPortRealSignalPtrs(S, 0);
00301         in_g   = ssGetInputPortRealSignalPtrs(S, 1);
00302         in_A   = ssGetInputPortRealSignalPtrs(S, 2);
00303         in_lb  = ssGetInputPortRealSignalPtrs(S, 3);
00304         in_ub  = ssGetInputPortRealSignalPtrs(S, 4);
00305         in_lbA = ssGetInputPortRealSignalPtrs(S, 5);
00306         in_ubA = ssGetInputPortRealSignalPtrs(S, 6);
00307 
00308 
00309         /* ... and to the QP data */
00310         problem = (SQProblem *) ssGetPWork(S)[0];
00311 
00312         H = (real_t *) ssGetPWork(S)[1];
00313         g = (real_t *) ssGetPWork(S)[2];
00314         A = (real_t *) ssGetPWork(S)[3];
00315         lb = (real_t *) ssGetPWork(S)[4];
00316         ub = (real_t *) ssGetPWork(S)[5];
00317         lbA = (real_t *) ssGetPWork(S)[6];
00318         ubA = (real_t *) ssGetPWork(S)[7];
00319 
00320         count = (real_t *) ssGetPWork(S)[8];
00321 
00322 
00323         /* setup QP data */
00324         nV = ssGetInputPortWidth(S, 1); /* nV = size_g */
00325         nC = (int) ( ((real_t) ssGetInputPortWidth(S, 2)) / ((real_t) nV) ); /* nC = size_A / size_g */
00326 
00327         for ( i=0; i<nV*nV; ++i )
00328                 H[i] = (*in_H)[i];
00329 
00330         for ( i=0; i<nC*nV; ++i )
00331                 A[i] = (*in_A)[i];
00332 
00333         for ( i=0; i<nV; ++i )
00334         {
00335                 g[i] = (*in_g)[i];
00336                 lb[i] = (*in_lb)[i];
00337                 ub[i] = (*in_ub)[i];
00338         }
00339 
00340         for ( i=0; i<nC; ++i )
00341         {
00342                 lbA[i] = (*in_lbA)[i];
00343                 ubA[i] = (*in_ubA)[i];
00344         }
00345 
00346         xOpt = new real_t[nV];
00347 
00348         if ( count[0] == 0 )
00349         {
00350                 /* initialise and solve first QP */
00351                 status = problem->init( H,g,A,lb,ub,lbA,ubA, nWSR,0 );
00352                 ssGetPWork(S)[0] = ( void* ) problem;
00353                 problem->getPrimalSolution( xOpt );
00354         }
00355         else
00356         {
00357                 /* solve neighbouring QP using hotstart technique */
00358                 status = problem->hotstart( H,g,A,lb,ub,lbA,ubA, nWSR,0 );
00359                 if ( ( status != SUCCESSFUL_RETURN ) && ( status != RET_MAX_NWSR_REACHED ) )
00360                 {
00361                         /* if an error occurs, reset problem data structures and initialise again */
00362                         problem->reset( );
00363                         problem->init( H,g,A,lb,ub,lbA,ubA, nWSR,0 );
00364                 }
00365                 else
00366                 {
00367                 /* otherwise obtain optimal solution */
00368                 problem->getPrimalSolution( xOpt );
00369                 }
00370         }
00371 
00372         /* generate block output: status information ... */
00373         out_objVal = ssGetOutputPortRealSignal(S, 0);
00374         out_xOpt   = ssGetOutputPortRealSignal(S, 1);
00375         out_status = ssGetOutputPortRealSignal(S, 2);
00376         out_nWSR   = ssGetOutputPortRealSignal(S, 3);
00377 
00378         out_objVal[0] = ((real_T) problem->getObjVal( ));
00379 
00380         for ( i=0; i<nU; ++i )
00381                 out_xOpt[i] = ((real_T) xOpt[i]);
00382 
00383         switch ( status )
00384         {
00385                 case SUCCESSFUL_RETURN:
00386                         out_status[0] = 0.0;
00387                         break;
00388 
00389                 case RET_MAX_NWSR_REACHED:
00390                         out_status[0] = 1.0;
00391                         break;
00392 
00393                 case RET_INIT_FAILED_INFEASIBILITY:
00394                 case RET_HOTSTART_STOPPED_INFEASIBILITY:
00395                         out_status[0] = -2.0;
00396                         break;
00397                 
00398                 case RET_INIT_FAILED_UNBOUNDEDNESS:
00399                 case RET_HOTSTART_STOPPED_UNBOUNDEDNESS:
00400                         out_status[0] = -3.0;
00401                         break;
00402 
00403                 default:
00404                         out_status[0] = -1.0;
00405                         break;
00406         }
00407 
00408         out_nWSR[0] = ((real_T) nWSR);
00409 
00410         /* increase counter */
00411         count[0] = count[0] + 1;
00412 
00413         delete[] xOpt;
00414 }
